race.description: Community Bank Ballan & District Ballan Cup Hcp (Bm78)
race.comment: FRIDGE MONSTER (8) was on a winning run of two races but last time out finished third over 1500m at this track. Well placed to return to best form. BRUNG KING (7) turned in a strong performance first-up when in the money at Bendigo but disappointed last time when tenth, beaten 10 lengths, at Sale over 1400m. That was an uncustomary poor run on Heavy ground, so we have to give him another chance if those conditions prevail. OTAGO (4) looked a world-beater early in his career and while he hasn't lived up to those raps for one reason or another, he'll be better for the first-up run and has a great second-up record (2:1-0-1). LIM'S IDA (1) third-up today and placed third-up previously. Include in wider plays.
